Real Estate Manager
Real Estate Manager
Location:  Singapore
A prestigious corporate and funds company is looking to recruit a real estate manager for its office in Singapore.
You will be responsible for the management and co-ordination of a significant real estate structure for a key client.
The role covers the full spectrum including corporate governance, company secretarial and full client relationship management.
The ideal candidate will need to be ACCA or ICPAS qualified with a very good educational background.
Mandarin and English languages are compulsory for the role.
An excellent working environment coupled with a competitive remuneration and benefits are on offer.
For further information please contact Gina Le Prevost on +41 (0)22 807 2022 or email your cv with any other relevant information to gina@ap-executive.com
